@startuml
actor Visitor
participant Frontend as "Main Page"
participant Backend as "Current Reading API"
participant Application as "Featured Reads Use Case"
participant Persistence as "Featured Reads Query Repository"
participant Database as "current_reading_posts"

Visitor -> Frontend: Open main page
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/v1/current-reading-posts/featured
Backend -> Application: list featured books
Application -> Persistence: load active current-reading titles
Persistence -> Database: select active current-reading posts
Database --> Persistence: active titles
Persistence --> Application: active titles
Application -> Application: normalize titles and aggregate reader counts
Application -> Application: rank top 3 books deterministically
Application --> Backend: featured books
Backend --> Frontend: 200 Featured books response
Frontend --> Visitor: Render hero panel above feed
@enduml

